  <ThingDef ParentName="BaseInvertebrate">
    <defName>Bloodspider</defName>
    <label>bloodspider</label>
    <description>A large, quadrupedal invertebrate with two small graspers tucked under their abdomen. They act primarily as scavengers, seeking out the weak or dying to drain them of their blood, hence their macabre name. Not an actual member of the arachnia genus, their true origins remain a mystery.</description>
